160
00:11:47,872 --> 00:11:48,919
in the market.

161
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,320
I hope you understand my point.

162
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:55,720
It's true that we don't have
a global reputation yet.

163
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,480
That's why we pay more attention

164
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,360
to feedback from market and needs of customers.

165
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,500
You said the Norwegian market

166
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:06,000
will reject Ruifeng,

167
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,480
but I don't think

168
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:10,280
any customer from any country

169
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,799
will reject innovation.

170
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,360
When change happens,

171
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,840
it's also when sortings are disrupted.

172
00:12:21,504 --> 00:12:22,528
Miss Chen.

173
00:12:23,879 --> 00:12:27,560
You are an attractive woman.

174
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:30,519
But, business is business.

175
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:34,960
We can only consent to international,
big, high-class brands.

176
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:37,919
So it does not matter

177
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:41,240
to lose a damn penny talking about anything.

178
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:42,880
I'm so sorry.

179
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,660
I still have something to do. I need to go.

180
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:51,639
And I hope we can have a chance
to cooperate in the future,

181
00:12:51,639 --> 00:12:53,440
but not now, I'm sorry.

182
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,519
Thank you.

183
00:12:54,519 --> 00:12:55,820
Thank you.

184
00:12:55,820 --> 00:12:56,919
Nice to meet you.

185
00:12:58,208 --> 00:12:59,328
Bye bye.

186
00:13:01,559 --> 00:13:03,120
This old man is really straightforward.

187
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,159
I'm sorry, Miss Mofei.

188
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,720
I couldn't help you.

189
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,720
Thanks to you, I got to know this news.

190
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,840
It's okay. I'll try harder.

191
00:13:41,399 --> 00:13:42,496
It's okay.

192
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,600
We can find another way.

193
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,879
I won't give up easily.

194
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,559
Any news from Mobai?

195
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:57,600
He was selected and will test-drive
Wings of Wind today

196
00:13:58,399 --> 00:13:59,488
for the final comparison.

197
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,904
But,

198
00:14:04,799 --> 00:14:06,200
the weather forecast in Shanghai

199
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,128
