00:41:37,419 --> 00:41:39,119
is the best choice for him.

554
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:43,400
How is he doing now?

555
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:46,000
You should go see him.

556
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,496
But I'm afraid

557
00:41:50,496 --> 00:41:51,559
if he sees me…

558
00:41:52,199 --> 00:41:53,440
The person he wants to see

559
00:41:54,599 --> 00:41:56,639
and lacks the courage to see the most

560
00:41:58,208 --> 00:41:59,264
is you.

561
00:43:05,267 --> 00:43:09,747
♫ The wind breathes quietly ♫

562
00:43:11,667 --> 00:43:16,271
♫ The heart gradually silences ♫

563
00:43:17,651 --> 00:43:24,239
♫ Your traces remain in my mind ♫

564
00:43:24,239 --> 00:43:29,327
♫ I can't delete them ♫

565
00:43:30,387 --> 00:43:36,399
♫ Time drips away bit by bit ♫

566
00:43:36,399 --> 00:43:43,279
♫ Memories are scattered everywhere ♫

567
00:43:43,279 --> 00:43:51,727
♫ The passing trees cast shadows like you ♫

568
00:43:52,563 --> 00:43:56,559
♫ Fading away ♫

569
00:43:57,715 --> 00:44:04,207
♫ Change the details bit by bit ♫

570
00:44:04,207 --> 00:44:10,575
♫ Decide our fate
in every second of every minute ♫

571
00:44:12,051 --> 00:44:18,927
♫ Just like the paradox of love ♫

572
00:44:18,927 --> 00:44:23,279
♫ The synchronization of heartbeats ♫

573
00:44:23,279 --> 00:44:29,647
♫ The surge of longing burns within ♫

574
00:44:29,647 --> 00:44:36,399
♫ Waiting to find the answer at the end ♫

575
00:44:36,399 --> 00:44:43,727
♫ Accelerating against the wind is your pride ♫

576
00:44:43,727 --> 00:44:53,327
